        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3729",
        "content": "Therefore it is not a paradox to say that the French would be wiser if they were less witty.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
